    "chapter": {
        "bookTitle": "Psalms",
        "delineation": "Chapter",
        "number": 101,
        "summary": "David sings of mercy and justice\u2014He will forsake the company of evildoers.",
        "chapterAugmentations": [],
        "verses": [
            {
                "text": "I will sing of mercy and judgment: unto thee, O Lord, will I sing.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "I will behave myself wisely in a perfect way. O when wilt thou come unto me? I will walk within my house with a perfect heart.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Jacob 6:12 (11\u201312).",
                        "start": 21,
                        "end": 27
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "I will set no wicked thing before mine eyes: I hate the work of them that turn aside; it shall not cleave to me.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 86,
                        "end": 88
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "A froward heart shall depart from me: I will not know a wicked person.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "HEB\u00a0perverse. Prov. 11:20; 17:20.",
                        "start": 2,
                        "end": 9
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Matt. 7:23.",
                        "start": 49,
                        "end": 53
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 63,
                        "end": 70
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Whoso privily slandereth his neighbour, him will I cut off: him that hath an high look and a proud heart will not I suffer.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Backbiting; Slander.",
                        "start": 14,
                        "end": 24
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Isa. 1:13.",
                        "start": 116,
                        "end": 122
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Mine eyes shall be upon the faithful of the land, that they may dwell with me: he that walketh in a perfect way, he shall serve me.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Walking with God.",
                        "start": 87,
                        "end": 94
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Perfection.",
                        "start": 100,
                        "end": 107
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 10,
                        "end": 18
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "He that worketh deceit shall not dwell within my house: he that telleth lies shall not tarry in my sight.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Deceit.",
                        "start": 16,
                        "end": 22
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Honesty; Lying.",
                        "start": 72,
                        "end": 76
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "I will early destroy all the wicked of the land; that I may cut off all wicked doers from the city of the Lord.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            }
        ]
    }
}